{"tid":1080012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近識咗個台灣女仔.....","createTime":"2019-03-27T10:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:28:17.000Z","uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"20ad982ce3bc4284985761e25a74995e98a3734d","tid":1080012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"最近識左個台灣女仔<br />\n傾計果時都知佢有男朋友 想分手<br />\n因為佢男朋友好食懶飛 最近一次仲打過佢<br />\n我知佢有抑鬱 仲食緊藥 所以日日都會陪住佢傾計<br />\n唔係想溝佢,因為始終隔住個海 溝黎無意思<br />\n一開始都係哥哥妹妹關係 訓之前都要講下晚安 發個好夢<br />\n平時傾計 思想、興趣 連鐘意食既野 同我太相近 開始對我有意思<br />\n有日佢同我表白 <br />\n我無諗太多就答應左 一黎覺得走到最後都會散<br />\n因為我好明白 點鐘意一個人都好 鐘意既能量用完 剩餘既係寂寞<br />\n而佢讀醫科要去醫院宿舍住 所以果段時間幾乎晚晚都視頻傾計到2,3點<br />\n我唔話要訓啦佢都唔願收線 <br />\n就算無野傾 佢都可以望住我咩都唔做 比我感覺係佢沈晒船<br />\n唔知係咪日子耐左,我都開始對佢有少少在意 有少少上心 開始鐘意佢<br />\n有傾過下將來點,其實問題不大 想做都可以做到<br />\n而我依加煩既地方係<br />\n黎緊會去台灣搵佢玩 仲要住埋同一間酒店 會有事發生 都唔係重點<br />\n重點係 佢未分手<br />\n以前發過誓唔要好似老豆咁樣仆街 如果我照做左,咁樣同我老豆有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我好想同佢講 對唔住,你未分手 我過唔到自己嗰關 原則問題<br />\n<br />\n故事打到黎依度 我諗由依加起要起返幅牆隔返開個距離<br />\n去到台灣最好分床訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得食唔食 罪大惡極萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653d33037b9d9664fdcccb53589049458213d74a","tid":1080012,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔知你咩樣，等我假扮你去見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc88245eca485e6e776aca2fe21491e1ba1b4ce","tid":1080012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"653d33037b9d9664fdcccb53589049458213d74a","tid":1080012,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔知你咩樣，等我假扮你去見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"當然知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n晚晚開cam傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8e62e2247086a0c4b3c8191b6dac1cc3df7598","tid":1080012,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc88245eca485e6e776aca2fe21491e1ba1b4ce","tid":1080012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"653d33037b9d9664fdcccb53589049458213d74a","tid":1080012,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔知你咩樣，等我假扮你去見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"當然知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n晚晚開cam傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"好快會收到勒索"},{"pid":"525d3a258fe8e7e0c48e9334e73ec031937213a3","tid":1080012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf8e62e2247086a0c4b3c8191b6dac1cc3df7598","tid":1080012,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc88245eca485e6e776aca2fe21491e1ba1b4ce","tid":1080012,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"653d33037b9d9664fdcccb53589049458213d74a","tid":1080012,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔知你咩樣，等我假扮你去見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"當然知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n晚晚開cam傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"好快會收到勒索"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"果個一定係肩肩send比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8281e50cd0784498e9319fcbb956dc5131beb1e","tid":1080012,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /